    <p align="left"><span class="qinfo">Description and Comments: </span>This one begins in
    the warrior's guild of Neriak and takes place in Lavastorm. There is a goblin runner that
    cross the Lavastorm rather quickly and fairly often. Kill him and he will carry a runner's
    pouch. This runner's pouch may be part of the larger Crushbone, Neriak storyline. The
    rangers chase down an orc runner in Butcherblock to intercept notes in between Crushbone
    and Neriak, I am not sure what plans you are meddling in here when you intercept this one.
    Ligge has received the pouch a few times, but he is not very welcome in Neriak. Must be
    all those guards he kills.</p>
