    <p align="left"><span class="qinfo">Description and Comments:</span> This quest is
    probably rogue only. It begins with Nabi in the Neriak rogues guild and will require you
    to first run to see Giz near the docks of Freeport, depending on your Freeport faction you
    may need to take the underground passages or sneak through invisible. Tell Giz that Nabi
    sent you and he will explain that you are needed to go kill the daughter of the Seafarer's
    Tavern owner. Her name is Lyda and she resides on the top floor of the tavern. As always
    check everyone you walk by some in here will kill many evil types. Bring her head back to
    Nabi and receive a possible ratskin cloak and some coins.</p>
