    <p align="left"><span class="qinfo">Description and Comments: </span>Loveal S´Nez is in
    the Lodge of the Dead and is tired of the goody goody paladins. In particular, the paladin
    Sir Lindeal. If you accept the offer from Loveal to perform a test you will need to go
    after Lindeal. He can be found in the Lavastorm Mountains and should be hunted down and
    killed. You will receive his Testimony Book and need to return it to S'Nez. Reward may
    include a damask robe. Completing this task opens the door for the Thex Mallet quest. You
    will be asked about appointed tasks and that happens to be the Mallet for the Queen. This will hurt PriestofLife, KnightsofThunder, GuardsofQeynos and improve
    Bloodsabers.</p>
