    <p align="left"><span class="qinfo">Description and Comments:</span> This comes from Yegek
    B'Larin in the arena and has two parts. First you take the bag he gives you and fill it
    with bone chips and beetle eyes and bring it back to him. This opens the door for part two
    BUT it does require you have your newbie nodrop sword as he does ask for it. When you give
    it to him a Tier'Dal traitor will appear you need to kill. You also need to do this
    unarmed! Most people get beat up by this guy badly. If you do complete it you will only
    get some minor item. So IMHO it's not worth it unless you just happen to have that crap
    nodrop sword and a maxed hand to hand skill when you go around level 6 or so to kill him.</p>
