    <p align="left"><span class="qinfo">Description and Comments: </span>Another rogue
    initiated quest. This will send you to Freeport dock area with a note and will require
    some sneaking. There are false walls along the West Freeport walls outside the city.
    Follow the wall each way and slide across it to find them. The one to the right of the
    gate will get you headed in the right direction. Once Bait Masterson is gone and night has
    arrived your contact will be there. The story is that the loot was lost overboard and you
    need to kill the shark down in the water. The chest gets returned to the rogue guild in
    Neriak. I have killed 4 sharks so far and no chest. However, the chest seems
    to be back underneath the shark now. Take it back to the rogue for reward.
    </p>
